{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Boorman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aimee Boorman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Boorman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Boorman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The move\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"her legs\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was almost kind of necessity is the mother of invention,\\\" Boorman told The Associated Press in 2015.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999994124664, \"rank\": 5.873187831828492e-10, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"necessity\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"the mother\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"invention\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"Boorman\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her calf was hurting.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her calf\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had bone spurs in her ankles and she's really good at floor with landings.\\\"\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bone\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"her ankles\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"floor\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"landings\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles returned to the sport in 2018 following a two-year layoff after winning the all-around at the 2016 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-year layoff\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Olympics\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not content to merely repeat herself, Biles began working on a triple-twisting, double flip that is now known simply as \\\" the triple-double.\\\"\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"a triple-twisting, double flip\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She unveiled it while winning the 2019 U.S. Championships then did it again at the world championships a few months later when she won the fifth of her record six world all-around titles.\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2019 U.S. Championships\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"her record six world all-around titles\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to see how it looked,\\\" she explained afterward.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As with a lot of gymnastics elements, Biles took a Cheng vault and added another layer of difficulty - this one an extra half twist on a vault originally done by China's Cheng Fei.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2716, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9998223892234128, \"rank\": 0.00012462381189271785, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2733, \"title\":