entence\": \"She began tinkering with it in 2021, but it's in the last year that it has morphed into perhaps the most show-stopping thing done in the sport.\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"perhaps the most show-stopping thing\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3438}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vault asks Biles to do a round-off back handspring onto the table, then two backward flips in pike position with her hands essentially clasped to her knees.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vault\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3468}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"a round-off\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"pike position\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"her hands\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3585}, {\"ngram\": \"her knees\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She does it with so much power, she can sometimes overcook it.\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much power\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the U.S. Olympic trials last month, it drew a standing ovation.\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic trials\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"a standing ovation\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No, it's not normal,\\\" longtime coach Laurent Landi said after she drilled it at the 2023 U.S. Championships.\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3789, \"end\": 3802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Landi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": 